RailsBatchYuiCompressor

UTF8 okay :P

YUI Compressor source : http://yuilibrary.com/
BatchYuiCompressor : http://code.google.com/p/batchyuicompressor/

use New BSD License : http://www.opensource.org/licenses/bsd-license.php

please change %PLUGIN%/lib/batchyuicompressor/compress.ini first
default

(JavaScript) %RAILS_APPS%/public/javascripts_source/ => %RAILS_APPS%/public/javascripts/
(StyleSheet) %RAILS_APPS%/public/stylesheets_source/ => %RAILS_APPS%/public/stylesheets/

& use it

rake yui_compress

